                </section>
                <section class="about-me-section">
                    <h2>About Me</h2>
                    <div class="about-me-content">
                        <div class="about-me-text">
                            <p>Hello! I'm John Ogletree, a passionate digital artist and designer with a knack for creating engaging user experiences and visually appealing digital products. My journey in design and development has equipped me with a unique blend of creative and technical skills.</p>
                            <p>I specialize in UI/UX design, focusing on user research, wireframing, prototyping, and usability testing to ensure that every product is not only beautiful but also intuitive and user-friendly. On the development side, I enjoy bringing designs to life with clean, efficient frontend code.</p>
                            <p>When I'm not designing or coding, you can find me exploring new digital art techniques, experimenting with generative art, or enjoying the outdoors in Martinez, GA.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="about-me-picture">
                            <div class="image-card-wrapper">
                                <div class="name-card">
                                    <h3>John Ogletree</h3>
                                    <p>Digital Artist & Designer</p>
                                </div>
